Package: fChange
Title: Functional Change Point Detection
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(
    person("Jeremy", "VanderDoes", , "jeremy.vanderdoes@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0001-9885-3073")),
    person("Gregory", "Rice", role = "aut"),
    person("Martin", "Wendler", role = "aut") )
Description: Change point detection for discretely observed, yet innately 
  functional data. Includes methods to process and investigate such data, including 
  functional ACF, smoothing, change point detection, plotting, and so forth.
